---
title: Mango Chicken Wraps with Green Pepper
description: Full of fresh, sweet and tangy flavour, our mango chicken wraps are the perfect recipe for busy evenings. With pan-fried chicken and fresh vegetables, you’ve got a light yet super satisfying dish!
